++++
Carp
++++

Summary
=======

Carp is a utility for code templates, using jinja2_.  It cuts down on
typing, so you won't get CARP-al tunnel.  Harharhar.

.. _jinja2: http://jinja2.pocoo.org

Example usage
=============

Try it like this::

    $ mkdir carpdir # your templates will go in here
    $ carp-list # you will get nothing back, since you have no templates
    $ carp-add some-file-that-already-exists
    $ carp-list # now you will see that file



